name: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival 2021
description:
Today marks the beginning of Mid-Autumn Festival and I thought I would celebrate by drawing a little Pokemon art!  It's one of my favorite holidays as it gives me a great excuse to eat Mooncakes.  So I hope everyone can enjoy their holiday and of course eat lots of yummy Mooncakes!!

HicEtNunc version has the Chinese characters on the image.  If you'd like it without the words you can purchase it on Kalamint for the same price.
